	   <tr><td colspan=2>I like your storytelling so far! Please keep writing, and we'll keep reading.<br><br>Cheers,<br>&nbsp;<br>Phreda Biggles<br>32 Warrior, Drunken Bandit<br><a href=HTTP://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/journal.html?user=122873 target=_new>Tales of a Halfling Tank Girl</a></td></tr>
